### ================================================
### RentalMS API Tests - VSCode REST Client
### Install extension: "humao.rest-client"
### ================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@ownerToken = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE
@tenantToken = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Dang nhap Owner
# @name loginOwner
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner@rentalms.com",
  "password": "owner123"
}

###

### 2. Dang nhap Tenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tenant1@rentalms.com",
  "password": "tenant123"
}

###

### 3. Dang ky nguoi dung moi
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newowner@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Chu Tro Moi",
  "phone": "0909000000",
  "role": "OWNER"
}

###

### 4. Lay danh sach khu tro (dung owner token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

###

### 5. Tao khu tro moi
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Khu Tro Test Quan 1",
  "address": "789 Nguyen Trai, Quan 1, TP.HCM",
  "description": "Khu tro test tu API",
  "publishStatus": "PUBLIC"
}

###

### 6. Tao phong don le
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/buildings/1/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNo": "TEST-01",
  "price": 3200000,
  "area": 25.0,
  "beds": 1,
  "amenities": "Wifi, Dieu hoa, Tu lanh",
  "description": "Phong test dep"
}

###

### 7. Bulk create 5 phong
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/buildings/1/rooms/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pattern": "B-{i}",
  "count": 5,
  "startIndex": 1,
  "price": 2800000,
  "area": 22.0,
  "beds": 1,
  "amenities": "Wifi, Nha ve sinh rieng"
}

###

### 8. Update GeoJSON polygon
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/buildings/1/shape
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "geoJson": "{\"type\":\"Polygon\",\"coordinates\":[[[106.69,10.77],[106.70,10.77],[106.70,10.78],[106.69,10.78],[106.69,10.77]]]}"
}

###

### 9. Publish khu tro
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/buildings/1/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PUBLIC"
}

###

### 10. Tao hop dong
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contracts
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 2,
  "tenantId": 4,
  "startDate": "2024-03-01",
  "endDate": "2025-03-01",
  "deposit": 6000000,
  "monthlyRent": 3000000,
  "rentCycle": "MONTHLY",
  "policy": "Dong tien truoc ngay 5 moi thang"
}

###

### 11. Xem danh sach hop dong (Owner)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contracts
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

###

### 12. Xem hoa don (Tenant)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bills
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantToken}}

###

### 13. Thanh toan hoa don
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bills/1/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 3150000,
  "method": "BANK_TRANSFER",
  "referenceCode": "TF2024031001",
  "note": "Thanh toan thang 3/2024"
}

###

### 14. Them khoan phi vao hoa don
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bills/1/items
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemType": "MAINTENANCE",
  "description": "Chi phi sua may lanh",
  "amount": 500000
}

###

### 15. Gui yeu cau bao tri
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/maintenance
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "description": "May lanh bi hong, chay yeu",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

###

### 16. Cap nhat trang thai bao tri
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/maintenance/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
  "note": "Da lien he tho sua, du kien hoan thanh 24h"
}

###

### 17. Tao invite token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/invites
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingId": 1,
  "permission": "VIEW",
  "expiryDays": 7,
  "maxUses": 10
}

###

### 18. Kiem tra invite token (public - khong can auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invites/validate/TOKEN_HERE

###

### 19. Tim kiem phong tren marketplace (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketplace?keyword=Binh Thanh

###

### 20. Xem thong tin tong quan API
GET {{baseUrl}}/
